media:group.media:title: [Speedrun Guide] Cook's assistant
media:group.media:description:
Got milk?
0. Opening the door of the mill and Fred's gate, wheat gate, dairy cow gate
1. Start and pick up the pot
2. Talk to Fayeth 3 __ 2 __ 1 _
3. Pick up Fred's egg
4. Pick wheat
5. Use the hopper and hopper controls
6. Fill the pot with flour
7. Milk the dairy cow
8. Home tele and finish
